{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 possible fruits and one goal, reach the Watermelon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your job is to combine matching fruits to evolve them to the next one and eventually reach the coveted Watermelon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To help you, you have 3 different abilities at your disposal. But watch out, using these will cost you some of your points. Be smart about when you use them to get the highest score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MULTIPLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Measure your fruit skills against another player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GET THE WATERMELON</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How many Watermelons can you combine before your basket overflows?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">USE YOUR ABILITIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Power, level up and destroy \u2014 These abilities will help you reach the Watermelon, using any of those will also allow you to angle your aim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GOLDEN FRUIT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If luck is on your side, you might even see the mysterious Golden Fruit. Find it and witness its effect firsthand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STATISTICS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Track your progress with in-depth statistics. Visit the menu to see the number of fruits you've combined, your ability usage, and much more. </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Game","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2658820/b78ca229a3146ac21a51299362b901de4ead98f8.jpg"},{"name":"100 Games","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2658820/30b731eb8947694a5ee03bc5e98c4ca84e5e8aaa.jpg"},{"name":"1000 Games","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2658820/9c3f38322032a24d4ffc3265aac0eb3c17f04e3b.jpg"},{"name":"1000 Points","path":"https:/